ent-RMCWindowCorsatReinforced-name = reinforced window
ent-RMCWindowCorsatReinforced-desc = A glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. It looks rather strong. Might take a few good hits to shatter it.
ent-RMCWindowCorsatReinforcedSecurity-desc = A red tinted glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. It looks very strong.
ent-RMCWindowCorsatReinforcedResearch-desc = A purple tinted glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. It looks quite strong. Might take some good hits to shatter it.
ent-RMCWindowCorsatHull-name = hull window
ent-RMCWindowCorsatHull-desc = A glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. This one has an automatic shutter system to prevent any atmospheric breach.
